README

This project is an online portfolio to demonstrate some of
my work and interests. Upon release of the website it will be a
fairly simple fixed width layout, primarily focusing on HTML5 and
CCS3 adherance. Further goals include creating a projects page and
adding a fluid layout.

Acknowledgements

The following are some great resources which I would like
to thank that were very helpful in making this site.

Extended footer from Joe Strong
http://www.joestrong.co.uk/blog/css-tip-extend-your-sites-footer-to-the-bottom-of-the-page/

Centering of website content from David Walsh
http://davidwalsh.name/center-website

Reset stylesheet from Eric Meyer
http://meyerweb.com/eric/tools/css/reset/

Tab menu and text alignment from Chris Coyier
http://css-tricks.com/tabs-with-round-out-borders/
http://css-tricks.com/pointer-events-current-nav/
http://css-tricks.com/left-align-and-right-align-text-on-the-same-line/

Color theme tools Kuler and Color Scheme Designer
https://kuler.adobe.com/#
http://colorschemedesigner.com/
